org.rocket.network

Interface Prop<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T -
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MutProp<T>

    public interface Prop<T>
    A Prop is an immutable delegation to another reference. Even if immutable, get() might not be constant. It kinda act like a C pointer.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods Default Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      T get()

      Retrieve the identifier of this prop.
      NetworkClient getOwner()
      Retrieve the owner of this prop.
      boolean isDefined()
      true if this prop holds a reference, false if not.
      default Optional<T> orEmpty()
      Retrieve the underlying reference and wrap it inside an Optional.

      Retrieve the underlying reference or null.
